Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(472,240)\bord0\shad0\fnsimhei\1c&HDDDFCE&\be1}是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(472,240)\bord0\shad0\fnsimhei\1c&HDDDFCE&\be1}否
